Description

  • TV Stand

This TV stand is solid and built to last. Its clean lines and compact design make it the perfect addition to a modern living room or media room. Thanks to its sleek design, this functional TV stand can be integrated seamlessly into your decor to create a smart entertainment space. The ample storage space lets you organize all your media and A/V devices in order to keep your space tidy. Additionally, an opening at the back facilitates access to electrical outlets.

63"W x 15.7"D x 21.8"H

  • MODERN DESIGN: With its minimalist design, clean architectural lines, as well as use of neutral colours and metal, this TV stand will give a modern look to any room.
